  <feature name="openengsb-infrastructure-jpa" version="${project.version}" description="OpenEngSB JPA Infrastructure">
    <details>
      This feature contains all require references to start an JPA environment as reuqired for the OpenEngSB Context. While
      this feature had been designed for the EDB it is also usable by other OpenEngSB core features and extended features
